WORLD OF COLOR

AT

DISNEYLAND RESORT AS WELL AS LABOR COST INFLATION.

SEGMENT OPERATING INCOME

SEGMENT OPERATING INCOME DECREASED 7%, OR $100 MILLION, TO $1.3 BILLION, DUE TO A DECREASE AT OUR DOMESTIC OPERATIONS, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY

AN IMPROVEMENT AT OUR INTERNATIONAL OPERATIONS.

