PROGRAMMING COSTS AND THE SYNDICATION CUSTOMER BAD DEBT CHARGE, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY HIGHER AFFILIATE FEES, INCREASED PROGRAM SALES AND LOWER MARKETING AND SALES EXPENSE.

