OPERATIONS AT THE DISNEY STORE NORTH AMERICA IN FISCAL 2009 WHEREAS FISCAL 2008 INCLUDED FIVE MONTHS OF COMPANY-OWNED OPERATIONS AND SEVEN MONTHS OF LICENSED OPERATIONS.

