EURO DISNEY  OTHER ADVANCES.

ADVANCES OF 331 MILLION ($451

MILLION AT OCTOBER 2, 2010 EXCHANGE RATES) ARE COLLATERALIZED BY CERTAIN HOTEL ASSETS AND BEAR INTEREST AT A FIXED RATE OF 3.0%. THE REMAINING ADVANCES OF 12 MILLION ($17 MILLION AT OCTOBER 2, 2010 EXCHANGE RATES) ARE

