PLAN

ASSETS

A SIGNIFICANT PORTION OF THE ASSETS OF THE COMPANYS DEFINED BENEFIT PLANS ARE MANAGED ON A COMMINGLED

BASIS IN A THIRD PARTY MASTER TRUST. THE INVESTMENT POLICY AND ALLOCATION OF THE ASSETS IN THE MASTER TRUST WERE APPROVED BY THE COMPANYS INVESTMENT AND ADMINISTRATIVE COMMITTEE WHICH HAS OVERSIGHT RESPONSIBILITY FOR THE COMPANYS

RETIREMENT PLANS. THE INVESTMENT POLICY RANGES FOR THE MAJOR ASSET CLASSES ARE AS FOLLOWS.

ASSET CLASS

MINIMUM

MAXIMUM

EQUITY INVESTMENTS

